WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.651
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.651 --> 00:00:04.539
Welcome to Unit 1, Welcome and Calendar.

3
00:00:04.539 --> 00:00:08.666
This unit has 70 vocabulary cards in 6 learning groups.

4
00:00:08.666 --> 00:00:11.142
Group 1 is Greetings and Introductions.

5
00:00:11.142 --> 00:00:15.682
Listen for words such as name, partner, like, spell, friend, hello.

6
00:00:15.682 --> 00:00:17.745
Group 2 is Calendar Words.

7
00:00:17.745 --> 00:00:22.285
Listen for words such as calendar, day, week, month, date, birthday.

8
00:00:22.285 --> 00:00:24.761
Group 3 is Words Around Us.

9
00:00:24.761 --> 00:00:28.888
Listen for words such as book, tablet, chart, picture, word.

10
00:00:28.888 --> 00:00:30.538
Group 4 is Colours.

11
00:00:30.538 --> 00:00:35.078
Listen for words such as red, blue, green, yellow, orange, purple.

12
00:00:35.078 --> 00:00:37.967
Group 5 is Numbers 1 to 12.

13
00:00:37.967 --> 00:00:42.506
Listen for words such as one, two, three, four, five, six.

14
00:00:42.506 --> 00:00:45.395
Group 6 is Order Words for Dates.

15
00:00:45.395 --> 00:00:49.934
Listen for words such as first, second, third, fourth, fifth, sixth.

16
00:00:49.934 --> 00:01:00.252
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

17
00:01:00.252 --> 00:01:03.140
You are ready to begin Unit 1.
